0.5.name: wordpress/eidogo-for-wordpress
0.5.description: EidoGo for WordPress makes it easy to embed SGF files in your WordPress-powered blog with the EidoGo SGF viewer and editor. If you write a blog about go (baduk, wéiqí, 碁, etc.) this plugin will let you easily post go diagrams, game records, problems, joseki dictionaries, etc. PHP 5 is required. Imagemagick is recommended but not required.
